    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"587349\">Trevor Gross</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/415254-DRM/topic/Duplicate.20symbols/near/438026564\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"671004\">Danilo Krummrich</span> did you ever wind up asking about that duplicate symbol, or finding out more?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I did not dig in more, but I asked about it in [1].</p>\n<p>[1] <a href=\"https://rust-lang.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/131828-t-compiler/topic/Linux.20kernel.3A.20duplicate.20function.20definition\">https://rust-lang.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/131828-t-compiler/topic/Linux.20kernel.3A.20duplicate.20function.20definition</a></p>",
        "id": 438391549,
        "sender_full_name": "Danilo Krummrich",
        "timestamp": 1715614408
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Another thing you can do is something along these lines:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">trait</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">DevresCompatible</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span> <span class=\"nf\">_devres_get_callback</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">extern</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"C\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c_void</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"fm\">macro_rules!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">impl_devres_compatible</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"cp\">$t</span>:<span class=\"nc\">ident</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CALLBACK</span>: <span class=\"nc\">extern</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"C\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c_void</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$crate</span>::<span class=\"n\">devres</span>::<span class=\"n\">devres_callback</span>::<span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"cp\">$t</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">DevresCompatible</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"cp\">#[inline(always)]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span> <span class=\"nf\">_devres_get_callback</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nc\">extern</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"C\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c_void</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"n\">CALLBACK</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 438603280,
        "sender_full_name": "Alice Ryhl",
        "timestamp": 1715701234
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Each type used with <code>DevRes</code> then invokes that macro. The <code>static</code> is guaranteed to not get monomorphized.</p>",
        "id": 438603419,
        "sender_full_name": "Alice Ryhl",
